  <brief_title>Quantification of Cannabinoids and Comparison to Post-Surgical Pain Medication Requirements and Surgical Outcomes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Quantification of Endo- and Phytocannabinoids With Comparison to Pain Medication Requirements and Surgical Outcomes for Patients Undergoing Abdominal Surgery for Cancer</official_title>
